A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Major Clint Morris and Captain Dee Morris upon their
2 retirement; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Major Clint Morris and Captain Dee Morris have long been recognized by the
4 citizens of Georgia for the vital roles they have played in law enforcement and their deep
5 personal commitment to the safety and welfare of the citizens of Paulding County, Georgia;
6 and
7 WHEREAS, the careers of Major Clint Morris and Captain Dee Morris spanned a combined
8 total of nearly seven decades, during which they worked with three sheriffs and rose through
9 the ranks in multiple divisions, including Captain Morris becoming the Assistant Commander
10 of the Juvenile Division and Major Morris becoming the Commander of the Courthouse
11 Security Division; and
12 WHEREAS, as the Commander of the Uniform Patrol Division, Major Clint Morris played
13 a key role in implementing speed detection devices and improving policies and equipment
14 procurement within the division; and
