34 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
35 recognize and commend Major Clint Morris and Captain Dee Morris for their efficient,
36 effective, unselfish, and dedicated public service to the State of Georgia; congratulate them
37 upon the grand occasion of their retirement; and extend the most sincere best wishes for
38 continued health and happiness.
39 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
40 to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to Major Clint Morris
41 and Captain Dee Morris.
